/ %x!!key% (double bang) is malformed — Variable.Resolve flags IsMalformed and refuses
/ to split (Name keeps the whole body, Property stays null). Read paths NotFound it;
/ write paths surface a typed InvalidVariableReference error. This goal exercises the
/ read path because PLang test goals can't easily catch typed write-time errors yet.
/ Failure-matrix row.
- set %x% = 'value'
- assert %x!!cost% is null
